{"ID":"20240620001507-6prw6n2","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f334","id":"20240620001507-6prw6n2","title":"Go项目中使用 Base64Captcha 快速实现网站的验证码功能，内置多种类型的验证码","type":"doc","updated":"20240620001522"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240620001522-49guqbv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-49guqbv","updated":"20240620001522"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在当今世界，网站的安全性变得越来越重要。验证码作为一种简单而有效的验证手段，已经被广泛应用于各种在线平台。Base64Captcha是一个开源的Go语言库，它提供了一个简单、灵活的方式来生成多种形式的验证码，包括数字、字母、数字字母组合、算术式、音频等形式的验证码。本文将深入讲解Base64Captcha库的使用方法和特点，帮助你在自己的项目中实现验证码功能。"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-4odwh4l","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-4odwh4l","updated":"20240620001522"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Base64Captcha的基本介绍"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-124q27a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-124q27a","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Base64Captcha是用Go语言编写的，利用此库可以轻松地为Web应用程序生成验证码。验证码的生成完全在服务器端完成，并以Base64编码的形式返回给客户端，这样可以减少服务器与客户端之间的数据传输量，并简化客户端的处理流程。"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-lq0k03o","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-lq0k03o","updated":"20240620001522"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安装Base64Captcha"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-oylypz9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-oylypz9","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在开始之前，确保你的开发环境已经安装了Go语言环境。可以通过以下命令安装Base64Captcha："}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-6jlpv8a","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-6jlpv8a","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"go get -u github.com/mojocn/base64Captcha\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-hcfesen","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-hcfesen","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安装完成后，你就可以在项目中引入并使用Base64Captcha库了。"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-nmxihry","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-nmxihry","updated":"20240620001522"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"创建验证码配置"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-qmqlwk1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-qmqlwk1","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Base64Captcha支持多种类型的验证码，每种类型的验证码都可以通过相应的配置来自定义其属性。以下是一些常见验证码类型的配置示例。"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-g3nmxva","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-g3nmxva","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数字验证码"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-kdq6e7e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-kdq6e7e","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数字验证码仅包含数字，你可以通过配置生成所需位数的数字验证码。"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-k1sq0ay","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-k1sq0ay","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"var configDigit = base64Captcha.ConfigDigit{\n    Height:     80,\n    Width:      240,\n    MaxSkew:    0.7,\n    DotCount:   80,\n    CaptchaLen: 5,\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-sxbz7d3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-sxbz7d3","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字母验证码"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-tbcc6h5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-tbcc6h5","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字母验证码仅包含字母，通过配置可以自定义验证码的长度、高度和宽度等属性。"}]},{"ID":"20240620001522-jrhh0uo","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240620001522-jrhh0uo","updated":"20240620001523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockF